data.description:
Get $500 off of the first month of rent when you sign lease before the end of the year. (Valid from 12/18/2023 till 12/31/2023)

Welcome/Bienvenido to your dream home! Step into this magnificent 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence, boasting a thoughtfully designed layout with brand-new hardwood floors and plush carpeting that add a touch of elegance to every room.

 Key Features:

Expansive open floor plan with cathedral ceilings
Abundant natural light from strategically placed skylights
Inviting fireplace in the spacious living room
Open dining room perfect for hosting gatherings
Culinary enthusiast's dream kitchen with gas stove and breakfast bar
Four well-arranged bedrooms and loft space on the upper level
Exceptionally spacious master bedroom with oversized master bathroom
Lower level ideal for an in-law suite with a bonus room, bedroom, and bathroom
Private entrance and deck for lower-level space
 Location:
Conveniently located near Sweetwater State Park, shopping centers, and I-20, this home is just under 30 minutes from downtown Atlanta and Hartsfield Atlanta Airport. Enjoy the perfect blend of luxury and accessibility.

 Recent Upgrades:

Recently painted kitchen for a fresh, modern look (Pictures coming soon)
Smart fingerprint lock on the main door for enhanced security
New dryer vent installation for improved functionality
Smart thermostat for efficient climate control
Home warranty included, covering repairs around the house.

We do not advertise on Craigslist. We will never ask you to wire money or pay with gift cards. Please report any fraudulent ads to us.

Renter is responsible for utilities. Garbage collections is prepaid until February 2024. Renter is responsable for lawn care as well as snow removal. Home warranty included on the rent. Small pets(up to 20 pounds) permitted. Only accepting a 6 months lease duration. Renter's insurance required.
